{
  "arquivo": "ed06_02_07",
  "total": 63,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(This is the place she specified.\\n Somewhere around here%p-2;――%p;)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(...Found her!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "???",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yo-Yotsuba.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "???",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You can hear me, right?\\nYotsuba, I came to see you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "???",
      "texto_en": "Too bad, huh, you've got the wrong person.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, I haven't.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "???",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Being silent is useless.\\nI'll say it as many times as it takes.\\nI like%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Sorry!\\nI need a timeout!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Eh...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "W-wait a minute!\\nWhy are you running away?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huff, huff... *wheeze*",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "A-are you okay?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huff... Huff...\\nI finally...cornered you...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "*sigh*",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What the...?\\nYou weren't actually running away, were you?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "If you were serious,\\nI would have lost sight of you a long time ago.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ahaha...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Damn it...\\nWhy did you run away?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Um, I didn't really run away.\\nI got a little confused, that's all.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But still, why run, then...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I thought I was mentally prepared.\\nBut...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "When you called my name, Uesugi-san,\\nI suddenly couldn't stay still anymore.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Put yourself in my shoes, who was left behind.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I'm really sorry.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Well then, let me say it again.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yotsuba.\\nI like you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Why, me? I mean?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Because there might be someone more \\nsuitable than me, Uesugi-san.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's not about being more suitable or anything.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I feel more at ease when I'm with you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Even when I struggled as a private tutor,\\nand during challenging school events...\\nI always felt like that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Even during this trip,\\nyou've been constantly concerned about me,\\nputting yourself aside.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "That's because...I wanted to support you,\\nand everyone else who was trying their best...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I'm here because you always supported me. ",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "However, this is my personal opinion.\\nSo%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yotsuba, tell me how you feel about me.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "...Uesugi-san,\\nare you honestly okay with someone like me?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Don't answer a question with another question.\\nBesides...you can probably imagine\\nhow I would answer, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I can more or less guess...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Well, that's good to hear.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But from my perspective,\\nI can't imagine how you would answer.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "However, there are words I want to hear from you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "What do you want me to say?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Well, that's obvious%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "'I also like you,' or something?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Really?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "My feelings are different, though.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I've always liked you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Uesugi-san.\\nI love you.\\nI have always, aaalwaaays...loved you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}